Class OrderedList<E extends java.lang.Comparable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • project3.OrderedList<E>

  • public class OrderedList<E extends java.lang.Comparable>
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a list which is comprised of nodes, each of which holds a comparable object and a link to the next larger node.
